item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - Beyoncé - 'Why Don't You Love Me (MK Ultras Remix)' in LOSSLESS?
item.description:
Hi all

I heard this ages ago and wondered if it was available somewhere in a lossless format? I know there was a video release (here on SM) and there's a CDR on Discogs, but from what I can tell, no streaming/download release. Can't seem to find it on TIDAL, which is weird as it's such a great remix...

There was a shorter radio/edit version floating around too I think.

Can anyone help? Thanks in advance
